headline: test-portfolio
tagline: Empowering users to make smarter trading decisions by delivering custom technical analysis tools with precision.
about: I'm a data scientist and tech entrepreneur passionate about turning ideas into impact. With a strong foundation in AI, trading strategies, and full-stack development, I build smart tools that simplify complex decisions. Whether it's automating SEO audits, designing trading indicators, or crafting seamless web experiences, I love creating systems that just work. Currently, I'm focused on building lean, scalable solutions that solve real-world problems. And this is my awesome testing portfolio!

portfolioProjects.title: 1. ClickCatalyst: AI-Powered Website Generator for Entrepreneurs
portfolioProjects.description:
ClickCatalyst lets users generate SEO-optimized, responsive websites with just a form. It uses AI to craft content, integrate branding, and deploy instantly with subdomain support. Aimed at freelancers and small businesses, the tool helps them go live in minutes—no coding or design skills required. Built with Next.js, Flask, AWS, and a custom webhook system for smooth automation.

portfolioProjects.title: SmartAudit: Python-Driven SEO Analyzer and PDF Report Generator
portfolioProjects.description: SmartAudit crawls any website using a Python backend powered by Puppeteer and BeautifulSoup. It analyzes technical SEO, mobile-friendliness, headings, word count, and more—then creates a shareable PDF. MongoDB stores minimal metadata, while full reports go to S3. portfolioProjects.title: BotRadar: Detecting Bot Behavior with Mouse Biometric Patterns
portfolioProjects.description: BotRadar identifies bots using human-like vs. inhuman mouse movement data. Built with Python, pandas, and GANs to synthesize and study patterns, it detects traits like perfect timing, robotic precision, and click bursts. It helps platforms flag suspicious sessions while allowing better user segmentation. portfolioProjects.title: SubTrack: In-Game Subscription Analytics for Gaming Studios
portfolioProjects.description: SubTrack tracks game subscription trends using event-level telemetry. It offers dashboards to monitor retention, engagement, churn, and revenue spikes. portfolioProjects.title: MarketPulse: A/B Testing Experiment Analyzer for Product Teams
portfolioProjects.description:
MarketPulse simplifies A/B testing insights with clear control vs. treatment analysis. It detects biases, flags novelty and carryover effects, and ensures proper randomization. The tool also generates downloadable summaries and charts. Built with Python and Plotly, it's tailored for product managers, marketers, and growth teams launching new features.
